Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation followed by Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Number of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation out of all Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that are preceded by SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that lead to a SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation from all SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that are followed by Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Average number of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that are followed by First Look-Please submit updates
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look-Please submit updates'

Name: Total First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation done by SYSTEM
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities == 'SYSTEM' where ma is the last value of performer

Name: Ratio of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation over SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Occasions how often the First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation is performed in relation to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation with subsequent Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of times SW-Reviewer Agreed is performed before First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Number of 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' activities for cases where activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation followed by First Look-Your updates are due in one week
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'First Look-Your updates are due in one week'

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation leading to a manuscript being assigned to a batch (Awaiting Assignment to Batch)
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'
